      "block_type_name": "ordered",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "VOC洞察 ",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "：大总管将指令发给 voc-analyst 。它自动抓取亚马逊竞品差评，得出结论：“用户痛点是承重不够和收纳麻烦。”",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgIP8pY8OXtBSKQOZJOrSr0p",
      "block_type": 13,
      "block_type_name": "ordered",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "GEO优化输出 ",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "：数据同步给 geo-optimizer 。它撰写产品独立站博客，为了迎合ChatGPT等AI搜索引擎，在文章中加入“承重450磅”等具体定量数据，并且明确引用了权威户外网站的评测来源。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgbP7QiTCgOhtzOq1DLSVt5e",
      "block_type": 13,
      "block_type_name": "ordered",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "Reddit流量劫持 ",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "：大总管同时唤醒 reddit-spec 。它去Google搜索老帖子，找到排名靠前的相关讨论帖。在老帖子下真诚评论，推荐我们的新款，强调其解决了老款的痛点，成功劫持长尾流量。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
