      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "首先，要在本地跑通这套协作，核心在于 OpenClaw 的路由隔离和通信放行。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgjHww3y5kFLXz0nQKMZtR8f",
      "block_type": 13,
      "block_type_name": "ordered",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "工作区物理隔离 ",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "：每个 Agent 必须有自己独立的 Workspace。 voc-analyst 的市场研报绝不能和 reddit-spec 的养号记录混在一个目录里。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgF9jfF6ovESShyQemUD5MuT",
      "block_type": 13,
      "block_type_name": "ordered",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "多账号长连接路由 ",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "：在飞书开放平台建5个独立应用，走 WebSocket 长连接。通过 openclaw.json 中的 bindings 数组，将飞书的 accountId 精准路由到对应的本地 Agent。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlg4RtaoMd6AbrO1EeXGsnDYg",
      "block_type": 13,
      "block_type_name": "ordered",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "A2A底层通信协议 ",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "：必须在 tools.agentToAgent 中开启白名单，这是让大总管能在后台发号施令的“唯一数据总线”。",
          "style": {
